---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="My Homelab | Daniel Castleberry" description="An overview of my personal cybersecurity homelab for research and practice.">
    <h1>My Cybersecurity Homelab</h1>
    <p class="intro">
        This is the virtual environment where I practice defensive and offensive security techniques, test new tools, and simulate real-world network scenarios.
    </p>

    <div class="diagram-placeholder">
        [ Network Diagram Coming Soon ]
    </div>

    <div class="lab-section">
        <h2>Purpose</h2>
        <p>The primary goal of my lab is to gain hands-on experience with enterprise-grade security concepts, including network monitoring, penetration testing, and incident response in a safe, isolated environment.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="lab-section">
        <h2>Hardware & Virtualization</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Host Machine:</strong> Dell OptiPlex with an Intel i7 and 32GB RAM.</li>
            <li><strong>Virtualization:</strong> Proxmox VE 8.0</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="lab-section">
        <h2>Virtual Machines</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Firewall:</strong> pfSense - Manages network segmentation and traffic rules.</li>
            <li><strong>Attacker VM:</strong> Kali Linux - Used for penetration testing tools.</li>
            <li><strong>Monitoring:</strong> Security Onion - A full SIEM for intrusion detection and log analysis.</li>
            <li><strong>Targets:</strong> A mix of vulnerable machines like Metasploitable2 and Windows 10 VMs for practice.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
<style>
    .intro { font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 60ch; }
    .diagram-placeholder {
        border: 2px dashed var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 4rem;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 2rem 0;
        color: #888;
    }
    .lab-section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    h2 { color: var(--accent-color); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    ul { list-style-type: square; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
</style>